    "description": "<p><span style=\"font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\">Ice permeates the earth and steals the enemy’s vital warmth. Each target hit by this spell suffers <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">【HR + 15】 ice</strong> damage and can’t burrow or emerge from the earth during their next turn. This spell can target creatures who are otherwise protected underground, but cannot target creatures who are flying, floating, falling, or otherwise in mid-air.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:10px 0px 0px;font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.45em;color:rgb(43, 74, 66);font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Opportunity</strong>: Each target hit by this spell suffers <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\"> @EFFECT[weak]</strong>.</span></p><hr /><p><strong>@LOSS[10 mp]</strong> for <strong>one</strong> target.</p><p><strong>@LOSS[20 mp]</strong> for <strong>two</strong> targets.</p><p><strong>@LOSS[30 mp]</strong> for <strong>three</strong> targets.</p>",
